title: Megalithomania 2011 Conference [15 MP4]
description:
2011 Megalithomania Conference in South Africa. 

International authors, visionaries and antiquarians share the latest cutting-edge research on the mysteries of the ancients. Graham Hancock, Andrew Collins, Antoine Gigal, Klaus Dona & Wayne Herschel, Hugh Newman, and Michael Tellinger to deliver a sensational account of what the ancients were up to. Two days, 7 speakers, 14 talks plus one panel discussion. Each video is approximately 1 hour in length.

Graham Hancock
Day 1: A Species With Amnesia: The Lost Civilization
Day 2: Elves, Aliens, Angels & Ayahuasca: Parallel Realms & The Vine Of The Dead

Klaus Dona
Day 1: Unsolved Mysteries Part 1
Day 2: Unsolved Mysteries Part 2

Andrew Collins
Day 1: Finding Eden - The Mystery Of The Gobekli Tepe
Day 2: Giza's Cave Underworld

Wayne Herschel
Day 1: Hidden Records BC
Day 2: Hidden Records AD

Antoine Gigal
Day 1: The Divine Island Of Giza
Day 2: The Mysterious Pyramids Of Mauritius

Michael Tellinger
Day 1: Vanished Gold Mining Civilization Of S.Africa
Day 2: Advanced Technology Of Ancient S. Africa

Hugh Newman
Day 1: Before The Maya: Olmecs & Megalithic Origins
Day 2: Earth Grids: Secret Patterns Of Gaia's Sacred Sites
